cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on geometric matching, which is a key step in computer vision tasks such as object recognition and image registration. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a learning-based method, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with homography transformation, which is a topic in computer graphics, suggesting that it could belong to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
